      "Knowing how to analyze a stock is crucial to make good investment decisions.",
      "The best investors in the world use a strict and rational framework to analyze stocks.",
      "In this article, I\\u2019ll teach you how to analyze stocks like a professional.",
      "Start reading about the company After you found a company which might be interesting, you should start with reading everything you possible can about the company.",
      "Let\\u2019s say that you want to analyze S&P Global. You start by looking at the following sources:",
